betterquesting:10.desc:8:
Everything about this place is strange. 
The call of Worthiness is incredibly inclusive, and it is not just limited to the Ascended. Basically every form that approximates a 'superlative', whether it be about power, force of will, or prowess, is called to Gallifrey.
Basically anything or anyone that is reaching a height in some aspect of reality is included in this call.
This seems to include animals and other non-sentient beasts. 
Here I will not see Chargers, I will Chargests.
